text: Cole Dickerson (born October 19, 1991) is an American professional basketball player for Egis Körmend of Hungarian League. ==Professional career== On August 2, 2016, Dickerson signed with Montenegrin club KK Mornar Bar. On December 9, 2016, he parted ways with Mornar after averaging 9.6 points and 3.6 rebounds per game in ten ABA League games.
